{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2180972, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 5498, "w": 858}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1627745215, "type": "image", "url": "qy/qyqgrki6lyojbvvttyzbsv4tr5k2xmnt.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2180982, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "刑拘，取保候审，正式逮捕，准备起诉，公审，宣判，二审，宣判，执行。我看没有一年下不来。最后即使罪名成立，也能来个驱逐出境", "timestamp": 1627745305, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2180985, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "alice好棒", "timestamp": 1627745353, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2180994, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我国国情是基本跑不了\n如果他真的有那种获得无罪判决的能力或权力 我们也没办法", "timestamp": 1627745415, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2180996, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "总之等到判决下达再喷他也来得及", "timestamp": 1627745446, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2180998, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "个人认为不会有反转", "timestamp": 1627745461, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2181002, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": 2180972, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 牛！", "timestamp": 1627745491, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2181053, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "按照我国国情，基本没跑了。你说的以及电视剧里都是“理论上的”，理论上存在，但是以我国国情，以及各级公检法机关为了维护公信力，你可以认为刑拘就等于马上坐牢（老妈法官，来自她的话）", "timestamp": 1627745794, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2181061, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": 2181053, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 这个“马上”，是指他坐牢是时间问题，但是因为法律有一套程序，从批捕到最后交付监狱，还有很多流程，这个需要花一些时间。", "timestamp": 1627745863, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2181076, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "按照这张图的话10日内就会逮捕", "timestamp": 1627745927, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2181084, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": 2181076, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: （需要审查是否符合逮捕条件，逮捕条件还是很严格的，我猜多半会取保候审", "timestamp": 1627745992, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2181102, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 422669, "reply_to": 2180972, "tag": null, "text": "附加判处驱逐出境的，必须在所判处的主刑执行完毕之后，再执行驱逐出境。人民法院一般是根据案件的具体情况，并兼顾我国与其所属国之间的关系，以及国际斗争的形势等，综合考虑是否适用。", "timestamp": 1627746095, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 422669, "reply": 12, "tag": null, "text": "有没有董哥董姐科普一下刑拘到判刑之间还差多少啊？根据我看的影视剧，拘留一段时间好像还有可能无罪释放是吗？不会给他跑了吧", "timestamp": 1627745099, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1627746093, "url": "", "vote": {}}}